    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows its age with several large dents, peeling clear coat, and noticeable rust around the wheel wells and door sills. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention for several leaks and a failing transmission. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts salvage.",
