    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that's been super well-loved? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it's in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. I've taken solid care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression and has had the double VANOS system professionally overhauled to ensure precise cam timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts smoothly, paired with a refreshed clutch and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary structural weak point. The suspension features upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining original geometry while sharpening turn-in response. Though the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with high-performance use, the drivetrain and thermal management systems are in peak operating condition. A true driver\u2019s specification for those who prioritize mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though a close inspection reveals minor road-wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear bumper, consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats are supple with minimal bolstering wear, and all original floor mats are included. Every electronic component\u2014from the high-definition infotainment screen and GPS navigation to the heated seats and ambient lighting\u2014is in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. I have maintained a comprehensive service folder, including a recent oil change, brake fluid flush, and a new set of air filters. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last year. It drives straight and true with no rattles or warning lights on the dash. This car has been my pride and joy, and it is ready for its next chapter with a new owner who appreciates a car that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a harmonious balance of performance and long-term reliability. The exterior maintains its original luster, complemented by an interior that reflects a history of careful ownership. Mechanically sound and having undergone a rigorous inspection process, this automobile is prepared for immediate service. We invite you to experience the caliber of this exceptional offering firsthand.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. If you\u2019re looking for something reliable and ready for your next adventure without breaking the bank, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one. It\u2019s a total gem that\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
