      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a 6-speed manual transmission. This example is mechanically sorted, boasting a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain remains tight, utilizing the factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. Performance is enhanced by a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein B6 dampers. While the Alpine White paint shows minor road-derived patina, the engine's compression is within factory spec and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) is razor-sharp. A driver-spec icon ready for the apex.",
